<HEADLINE>
NO LIMIT: THE COSTS OF GLOBAL AIDS 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 By DONALD G. McNEIL Jr.   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
