<HEADLINE>
ALL THAT'S BARE IS FIT TO WEAR 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing)  (The Week in Review)  
 By JENNY LYN BADER  
 
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
