<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TECH-CENTERPIECE0704-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Delete PC fear
 &HT;    By Frances Katz
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
