<P>
   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   Learn about endangered species and biodiversity while playing
along on the World Wildlife Fund's Web site. The Fun Stuff section
has loads of facts that will teach you about wildlife and issues
that affect our planet. Go to www.worldwildlife.org/fun/ to get
started.
</P>
