</P>
<P>
   ``He thinks that stuff's for sissies.'' (An unnamed fund-raiser
on George W. Bush's attitude to speech-coaching and teleprompters.
Washington Post, June 25) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; REFORMER WITH RESULTS?: &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   Some 56 percent of Texans support Bush for president; but 63
percent of them ``are unable to name any reforms that Bush has
brought about in his state.'' (Scripps Howard Texas poll, June 25) &QL;
