 &HT;    A second rover, the TerminatorBot, has arms that unfold so they
can drag the rover along or pick up objects _ ideal for exploring
loose wreckage for survivors after an earthquake, Voyles believes.
 &HT;    -----
 POET OF THE PILL  
 &HT;    Working at Syntex, a private company in Mexico City, chemist
