   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-ELECTION (Mexico City) _ On Sunday's electoral defeat of
the Institutional Revolutionary Party that has governed Mexico for
more than 70 years. By Sam Dillon.
</P>
<P>
   With a grpahic.
</P>
<P>
   With
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-FOX (Mexico City) _ A profile of the president-elect,
Vincente Fox. By Sam Dillon.
</P>
<P>
   And
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-ASSESS (Mexico City) _ News Analysis: On the political
earthquake that shook Mexico in Sunday's election and the new
political order that will likely follow. By Julia Preston.
</P>
<P>
   And
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-REACT (Dateline to come) _ Reactions from Mexicans to the
results of Sunday's election. By Ginger Thompson.
