<P>
   ECOM-PHILLY-TECH _ when Philadelphia was omitted from a Wall
Street Journal list of the top 20 technology areas last November,
the slight touched off a quest for attention that would have made
the region's Quaker settlers twitch uncomfortably. Civic leaders in
