<SLUG> BC-MEANS-COLUMN-$ADV05-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;     BOY SCOUT VALUES 
</HEADLINE>
  
 &HT;     (For release Wednesday, July 5)   &HT;     (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 &HT;     By MARIANNE MEANS  
 &HT;     c.2000 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
