 &UR; NETWORTH (COLUMN) _ &LR;  Perhaps biotech companies should develop an
ulcer medication for their shareholders. Seventeen of the top 20
mutual funds for the second quarter ended Friday were biotech or
health care funds, according to Morningstar. But that doesn't mean
their shareholders got a good night's sleep.  &UR; COLUMN BY &LR; 
 &UR; KATHLEEN PENDER &LR;
